      Constructors in javafx.scene with parameters of type SceneAntialiasing  
      Constructor 描述
      Scene​(Parent root, double width, double height, boolean depthBuffer, SceneAntialiasing antiAliasing)
      构造由根组成的场景，宽度和高度的尺寸指定是否为此场景创建深度缓冲区，并指定是否请求场景抗锯齿。
      SubScene​(Parent root, double width, double height, boolean depthBuffer, SceneAntialiasing antiAliasing)
      Constructs a SubScene consisting of a root, with a dimension of width and height, specifies whether a depth buffer is created for this scene and specifies whether scene anti-aliasing is requested.
